 <span class="hero__eyebrow">About CoreFlow</span>
 <h1 class="hero__title">Infusion care that puts value first.</h1>
 <p class="hero__lead">CoreFlow Specialty Infusion exists because home infusion in South Carolina needed a different model — one that measures success by what prescribers, patients, and payers actually receive, not by what a pharmacy provides.</p>
 </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
 <div class="container">
 <p class="lead">We are a non-compounding, non-retail specialty infusion pharmacy. We receive commercially manufactured medications, maintain them under pharmaceutical-grade cold chain conditions, and dispatch credentialed registered nurses to patient homes for administration. That's our model. It's specific by design.</p>
 <h2 class="section-title mt-6">Why we built CoreFlow.</h2>
 <p>Prescribers referring home infusion patients in South Carolina have historically faced the same set of problems: poor communication from pharmacy partners, inconsistent nursing quality, and referral processes that create more work than they eliminate.</p>
 <p>CoreFlow was built to solve those problems specifically — not to be a retail pharmacy, not to be a staffing agency, and not to be a compounding operation. We do one thing: specialty infusion in the home, done well, in South Carolina.</p>
 <p>Our structure is intentional. Credentialed, supervised nurses — not unsupervised staffing fills. Pre-manufactured medications, not compounded. One state, not a national footprint that treats South Carolina as a market segment.</p>
 <p>That approach earned us the trust of MUSC Health — <strong>a preferred home infusion partner for MUSC Health</strong>. When a major academic health system holds you to their clinical standards, it shapes how you build everything else.</p>
 <p>CoreFlow was established as a joint venture with Council Capital, a healthcare-focused private equity firm. </p>
 </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
 <div class="container">
 <div class="callout-dark">
 <span class="eyebrow" style="color:#bde4eb">MUSC Health Partnership</span>
 <h2>Chosen by MUSC Health.</h2>
 <p>a preferred home infusion partner for MUSC Health. </p>
 <p>MUSC Health is South Carolina's only comprehensive academic medical center. Their clinical and operational standards for home infusion partners are rigorous. Being a preferred home infusion partner for MUSC Health means CoreFlow has been evaluated against those standards and selected.</p>
